critique:
This document is an executive order that changes the organization of Customs Collection District No. 26 (Arizona). It revokes the designation of Ajo, Arizona, as a customs port of entry and designates Sonoyta, Arizona, as a customs port of entry. This seems like a fairly routine administrative action with minimal political implications.
